	(pch_source): Tweak.
	(pch_build): Key off a built file.
	(pch_output rule): Rename to...
	(pch_input rule): ...this.  Produce ${pch_output_builddir}
	instead of ${pch_output}.
	(install-pch rule): Install ${pch_output_builddir}.
	* include/Makefile.in: Regenerated.

